@Security_Authentication_HostAddress = http://localhost:5037

@TenantId = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

### Password Login
POST {{Security_Authentication_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/password/login
X-Tenant-Id: {{TenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"username": "demo",
	"password": "demo"
}

### OIDC Challenge (stub)
GET {{Security_Authentication_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/oidc/stub/challenge
X-Tenant-Id: {{TenantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### OIDC Callback (stub)
GET {{Security_Authentication_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/oidc/stub/callback?code=external-sub-1&state=PLEASE_FILL_FROM_CHALLENGE_REDIRECT
X-Tenant-Id: {{TenantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Refresh
POST {{Security_Authentication_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/token/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"refreshToken": "PLEASE_FILL"
}

### Token Revoke (single refresh token)
POST {{Security_Authentication_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/token/revoke
Authorization: Bearer PLEASE_FILL_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"refreshToken": "PLEASE_FILL_REFRESH_TOKEN",
	"allDevices": false
}

### Logout (all devices)
POST {{Security_Authentication_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer PLEASE_FILL_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"refreshToken": null,
	"allDevices": true
}

